<!--
	VONG QUAY MAY MAN
	- Config: Thiet lap vong quay
		- Activate: Kich hoat vong quay
		- LimitLevel: Gioi han cap do
	- Requiration: Yeu cau quay
		- RequireToken: Yeu cau dong cho moi luot quay
		- RequireBoundToken: Yeu cau dong khoa cho moi luot quay
		- RequireItemID: Yeu cau ve quay may man
	- Time: Thoi gian su kien
		- WeekDays: Cac ngay trong tuan (0: Chu nhat, 1: Thu 2, ..., 6: Thu 7), ngan cach boi dau ;
		- Times: Cac moc thoi gian mo, ngan cach boi dau ;
		- Duration: Thoi gian duy tri (mili-giay)
	- CellData: Du lieu o quay (phai co chinh xac 28 o)
		- Cell: Thong tin o vat pham
			- ItemID: ID vat pham
			- Quantity: So luong
			- RateUsingToken: Ty le quay vao neu su dung dong (phan 10.000)
			- RateUsingBoundToken: Ty le quay vao neu su dung dong khoa (phan 10.000)
			- RateUsingCard: Ty le quay vao neu su dung the (phan 10.000)
			- CheckPoint: Khi so luot quay dat cac nguong tuong ung moi quay vao o nay, ngan cach boi dau ; (-1 neu khong ap dung)
			- NotifyAfterTaken: Thong bao khi nhan
			=> Khi co CheckPoint thi Rate se luon luon la 0%
			- EffectType: mau sac cua vong tron xoay quanh (-1 la khong co gi) mau tu 1-7
-->
